      "message": "I stepped away from this problem for a while and let it simmer, then realized the problem with my earlier trial--I should be laundering EVERY allocation inside fStorage. Once I do that, GCC is satisfied at -O3, and it satisfies all the documented launder requirements. I\u0027ll amend this CL now.",
